import re,requests
def GetLSProData(page_data,Cookie_Jar,m):
 count=3;pn=1;data=[]
 while pn <= int(count):
     page='https://verteleseriesonline.com/network/netflix/page/'+str(pn)+'/';source=requests.get(page).content.decode('ascii','ignore')
     data +=re.findall('(?s)tip" rel=".*?"(http.*?)".*?lazy".*?"(http.*?)".*?tt">(.*?)<',source);pn +=1
 video = []
 for item in data:
     video += [(item[2], item[0], item[1])]
 return sorted(video)
]]></expres>
